Kafka 软件配置 SSL 证书
━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━
Kafka 软件配置 SSL 证书需要使用如下要素:

    •  /path/to/file.cer                         CA 机构颁发的权威证书文件
    •  /path/to/file.pem                         CA 机构颁发的 SSL 公钥证书文件
    •  /path/to/file.key                         CA 机构颁发的 SSL 私钥证书文件
    •  (A ∈ ca_domain) ∧ (PTR ∈ ca_domain)       CA 机构颁发的权威证书文件的认证域能够覆盖 A/ PTR 域名解析记录

""""""""" 使用 openssl 工具为 Kafka 软件创建密钥库文件
[root ~]# openssl pkcs12 -export \
                         -name kafka \
                         -in /path/to/file.pem \
                         -inkey /path/to/file.key \
                         -out /etc/kafka/kafka.keystore.p12 \
                         -password pass:season_4U
[root ~]# keytool -list -keystore /etc/kafka/kafka.keystore.p12 -storepass season_4U
Keystore type: PKCS12
Keystore provider: SUN

    Private key entry kafka
    Certificate fingerprint (SHA1): 5C:16:54:F4:E2:06:05:99:C4:77:C8:C0:74:20:25:92:0F:51:79:90
--------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------- ✻

""""""""" 使用 keytool 工具为 Kafka 软件创建信任库文件
[root ~]# keytool -import \
                  -noprompt \
                  -trustcacerts \
                  -alias ca@kafka \
                  -file /path/to/file.cer \
                  -keystore /etc/kafka/kafka.truststore.jks \
                  -storepass season_4U
[root ~]# keytool -list -keystore /etc/kafka/kafka.truststore.jks -storepass season_4U
Keystore type: JKS
Keystore provider: SUN

    Trusted cert entry ca
    Certificate fingerprint (SHA1): DF:3C:24:F9:BF:D6:66:76:1B:26:80:73:FE:06:D1:CC:8D:4F:82:A4
--------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------- ✻

""""""""" 维护主配置文件内的 SSL 配置项
[root ~]# vim /etc/kafka/server.properties
... ...
advertised.listeners=PLAINTEXT://kafka-0.season.com:9092,SSL://kafka-0.season.com:9093
listeners=PLAINTEXT://0.0.0.0:9092,SSL://0.0.0.0:9093
listener.security.protocol.map=PLAINTEXT:PLAINTEXT,SSL:SSL
inter.broker.listener.name=PLAINTEXT
ssl.keystore.location=/path/to/kafka.keystore.p12
ssl.keystore.password=season_4U
ssl.keystore.type=PKCS12
ssl.truststore.location=/path/to/kafka.truststore.jks
ssl.truststore.password=season_4U
ssl.truststore.type=JKS
ssl.enabled.protocols=TLSv1.2
ssl.endpoint.identification.algorithm=HTTPS
[root ~]# systemctl restart kafka.service
--------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------- ✻

